      {n:'Abd Rabbuh Mansur Hadi', r:'President of Yemen since 2012, governing from exile', e:'🏛️'},
      {n:'Al-Hamdani', r:"10th-century poet and geographer — 'the tongue of the Arabs'", e:'📜'},
      {n:'Ayat Al-Qurmezi', r:'Yemeni poet and Arab Spring activist, imprisoned for her protest poems', e:'✍️'},
      {n:'Nadia Murad', r:"(Yazidi from Iraq, near Yemeni border region context) — Nobel Peace laureate — use with care; better: Tawakkol Karman — Yemen's Nobel Peace Prize laureate (2011)", e:'🕊️'}
